  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A droplet of acid streaks from your pointing finger towards a creature you choose within range then explodes with a soft hiss into a pool of acid. Make a <strong>ranged spell attack</strong> against the target. The target takes <strong>8d4 acid damage</strong> on a hit, or half as much damage on a miss.</p><p><strong><em>At Higher Levels:</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the damage increases by 2d4 for each slot level above 3rd.</p>",
